name: blkd-outfit
description:
there were a few blacked themed LORAs. I wanted to take a crack, and try my own out.

I noticed most of them were more focused on anime girls, I wanted mine to be focused on realism.

Here are the prompts to use:

  • RealisticVision is awesome for this

  • 512x768, 512x512, or 768x768

  • CFG at 6 for better skin, bad text on clothing, and CFG at 8 for better text on clothing, but slightly bad skin (can easily clean this with inpainting)

  • Prompts to use: (blkd-outfit, bra, panties, thong, 1girl, brown haired Caucasian woman)
